beginning, the end.

00:50:13.760 --> 00:50:16.510
The same poem in Latvian.

00:50:16.510 --> 00:51:09.120
[ Foreign language ]

00:51:09.120 --> 00:51:14.980
Wolf One-Eye has changed,
he felt he had changed.

00:51:14.980 --> 00:51:16.620
He wasn't sure how.

00:51:16.620 --> 00:51:20.830
He could hardly remember
how it all once had been.

00:51:20.830 --> 00:51:24.390
