00:52:29.980 --> 00:52:34.010
But then a half will
just be half of a half,

00:52:34.010 --> 00:52:38.280
half of which half
I only half of them.

00:52:38.280 --> 00:52:44.310
All will be half days, half hours,
half baked, half done, halfhearted,

00:52:44.310 --> 00:52:49.060
